<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="lo">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ລຸ້ນໂຊກຮັບເງິນລ້ານ</title>
    <style>
        body {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
            margin: 0;
            background-color: #f0f2f5;
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
        }

        #gift-box {
            font-size: 100px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }

        #gift-box:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1);
        }

        #result {
            display: none;
            animation: popUp 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.175, 0.885, 0.32, 1.275);
        }

        h1 { color: #d32f2f; }
        .amount { 
            font-size: 3rem; 
            color: #ff9800; 
            font-weight: bold;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px #000;
        }

        .prank-note {
            margin-top: 20px;
            color: #777;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        @keyframes popUp {
            0% { opacity: 0; transform: scale(0); }
            100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <div id="gift-box" onclick="openGift()">🎁</div>
        <div id="result">
            <h1>ຍິນດີດ້ວຍ! ທ່ານໄດ້ຮັບລາງວັນໃຫຍ່</h1>
            <div class="amount">1,000,000,000 ກີບ</div>
            <p class="prank-note">(ນີ້ເປັນພຽງການຢອກຫຼິ້ນຊື່ໆເດີ້! 555+)</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        function openGift() {
            document.getElementById('gift-box').style.display = 'none';
            document.getElementById('result').style.display = 'block';
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
